OL,3,CAppeal for witness who gave pub
OL,4,Clandlord advanced life support to come
OL,5,Cforward
OL,7,FPolice are appealing for more
OL,8,Fwitnesses to come forward after pub
OL,9,Flandlord Matt O'Gara was allegedly
OL,10,Fassaulted in Lichfield city centre
OL,11,Flast month and later died.
OL,13,FPolice were called at 11.25pm on
OL,14,FSunday 24 May to Ricco and Loren bar
OL,15,Fon Market Street following reports
OL,16,Fthat a man had been punched.
OL,18,FMatt O'Gara, 31, was taken to hospital
OL,19,Fwith serious injuries but died on
OL,20,FTuesday 26 May.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/2
